  "***A POWERFUL MAGICAL SEAL IS BLOCKING YOUR PATH TO VICTORY***": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "***強力な魔法の封印が、あなたの勝利への道を阻んでいる***",
